  <brief_title>Effects of Systematic Patient Feedback on Therapy Outcome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Systematic Patient Feedback on Therapy Outcome and Dropout: A Randomized Controlled Study on Adult Out-patients at a Community Mental Health Centre.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
